<paragraph id="8BE3B605994BFFF007E3FD7AF7B3FCE9" blockId="0.[1266,2146,760,1393]" pageId="0" pageNumber="444">• Fairly small to very large ruminants with hollow horns in males or in both sexes with a bony core, growing directly from the skull, and toes encased in sturdy hooves.</paragraph>
